definition.en:
True means that it is shown on top of the community.
see [Lemmy protocol docs.](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/lemmy_protocol.html) and [Lemmy documentation](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/overview.html)
definition.de:
True bedeutet, daß es oben in der Community angezeigt wird.
siehe [Lemmy protocol docs.](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/lemmy_protocol.html) and [Lemmy documentation](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/overview.html)
definition.fr:
True signifie qu'il est affiché en haut de la communauté.
voir [Lemmy protocol docs.](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/lemmy_protocol.html) and [Lemmy documentation](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/overview.html)
definition.es:
True significa que se muestra en la parte superior de la comunidad.
ver [Lemmy protocol docs.](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/lemmy_protocol.html) and [Lemmy documentation](https://join-lemmy.org/docs/en/federation/overview.html)
